# USDM v4

This site provides reference documentation for the USDM v4 schema derived from the CDISC DDF-RA [dataStructure.yml](https://github.com/cdisc-org/DDF-RA/blob/aa303cb32f5d3ceecc68a16803e26720d2c1fc26/Deliverables/UML/dataStructure.yml) source model. It is intended to make the model easier to explore through browsable documentation for classes, slots, types, relationships, and example instances.

Use this site to understand the overall structure of the model, inspect class and slot definitions, review example instances, and navigate from high-level study concepts to the detailed attributes captured in the LinkML representation.

For cross-cutting implementation considerations and non-normative suggestions that apply across multiple trial design mapping pages, see [General Considerations](sdtm-mapping-considerations.md).

